<p>
<lb n="1"/>¿ lakṣmīlakṣitavakṣasaḥ kṣitibhṛtāṁ cōḍasya cūḍāma
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṇēḥ krīḍālōḍitagauḍakuṁtalakubhṛtsēnārnnavō
<lb n="3" break="no"/>bhūtsutaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> goṁka<unclear>ḥ</unclear> śśaṁkarapādapaṁkajarajōdājī
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ru<unclear>ja</unclear>tkuṁtalaḥ kāṁtā tannṛpatērvilāsavasatissabbā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṁbikā rājatē [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1*] śākābdē maṇibāṇakhēṁdugaṇi
<lb n="6" break="no"/>tē dākṣiṇyapuṇyāyanē śrīnādiṁḍlanivāsinē
<lb n="7"/>murabhidē lōkatrayasvāminē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> prādāddīpamakhaṁḍavarttima
<lb n="8" break="no"/>tulaṁ sā sabbamāṁbā satī yaddīpātkamalēkṣaṇaspa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nitarāṁ dhattē tri<unclear>nē</unclear>traśriyaṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*]
<lb n="10"/>svasti śrīśakavarṣaṁbulu 1055 gunēṁṭi dakṣiṇāya
<lb n="11" break="no"/>naṁbunaṁdu nādiṁḍlakēśavadēvaraku śrīmanmahāmaṇḍa
<lb n="12" break="no"/>lēśvaravelanāṁṭigoṁkaya priyasatiyaina sa
<lb n="13" break="no"/>bbama peṭṭina yakhaṁḍadīpaṁbunaku niccina goṟi
<lb n="14" break="no"/>yalu 55 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vīniṁ jēkoni niḍu<unclear>da</unclear> yiṟiyana koḍuku
<lb n="15"/>cāmenabōyuṁḍu nitya māneṁḍu neyi vōsi tana pu
<lb n="16" break="no"/>trānupautraka mī yakhaṁḍavarttidīpaṁbu naḍapaṁgalavāṇu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

